<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <!-- Updated: 2026-01-03 -->
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SEEN</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="./favicon.png" />
  <link rel="manifest" href="./manifest.json" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f3f6fc;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #0f1b33;
      --text-muted: #5f6b7a;
      --accent: rgba(166, 55, 11, 1);
      --accent-hover: rgba(130, 40, 5, 1);
      --border-subtle: #dce3ee;
      --radius-lg: 20px;
      
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html, body {
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      min-height: 100dvh;
      background: var(--bg);
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
        Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Open Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-main);
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 32px 16px 40px;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .page {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 28px 24px 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(180, 195, 215, 0.35);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .page {
        padding: 22px 18px 20px;
        border-radius: 16px;
      }
    }

    .logo-wrap {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .logo-wrap img {
      height: 60px;
      width: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    p { margin: 8px 0; font-size: 0.98rem; color: #0f172a; }

    ul { margin: 8px 0 0 1.1rem; padding: 0; color: #0f172a; font-size: 0.98rem; }

    li { margin-bottom: 6px; }

    .hero {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      padding-bottom: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .hero h2 { margin-top: 14px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

    .section {
      padding-top: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .section:last-of-type {
      border-bottom: none;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }
       .buttons {
      margin: 18px 0 6px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .buttons a,
    .buttons button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.24);
      transition:
        background-color 0.16s ease,
        color 0.16s ease,
        transform 0.08s ease,
        box-shadow 0.16s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .buttons a:hover,
    .buttons button:hover {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
    }

    .buttons a:active,
    .buttons button:active {
      transform: translateY(1px);
      box-shadow: none;
    }

.inline-icon {
  width: 1em;
  height: 1em;
  vertical-align: -0.2em;
  margin-right: 0.2em;
}


    .tiny { font-size: 0.76rem; margin-top: 6px; color: var(--text-muted); }

    footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    footer a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="page">

    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <img src="assets/seen-logo.png" alt="SEEN logo">
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>SEEN: Be heard. Be believed.</h1>
      <p>
        Tired of doctors who don't listen?<br>
        Been told "it's all in your head" one too many times?<br>
        Always forget to mention what matters most?
      </p>
      <p><strong>There's something that changes everything.</strong></p>
      <p>
        Walk into appointments with a printed summary that makes doctors sit up and pay attention. It sounds
        simple—but it's transformative.
      </p>
      <p>
        Hand your doctor a clear, organized summary before the appointment starts. Your timeline, symptoms,
        treatments, and why you're there—formatted so that they can scan it in under a minute. Easy to read, impossible to ignore.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Who It's For</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>People with complex conditions doctors don't understand</li>
        <li>Anyone who's struggled for years to get diagnosed</li>
        <li>Patients who aren't listened to or taken seriously</li>
        <li>Those whose appointments always feel rushed</li>
        <li>Anyone tired of not being heard</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>SEEN is for people who deserve better care.</strong></p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Use SEEN like an app</h2>

     

      <p>To install like an app: After clicking the open button, click <strong>Share <img class="inline-icon" src="assets/share-icon.svg" alt="Share icon"> → Add to Home Screen</strong> on iPhone/iPad, <strong>Menu → Install App <img class="inline-icon" src="assets/install-icon.png" alt="Install icon"> / Add to Home Screen</strong> on Android/Chrome, or <strong>Install <img class="inline-icon" src="assets/install-icon.png" alt="Install icon"> / Menu (⋮) → Install App</strong> on desktop Chrome/Edge. A SEEN icon will be added to your home screen or apps list.</p>
       <div class="buttons">
        <a href="https://leormug.github.io/seen-site/app/?v=0.6.0">Open SEEN</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      Created by patients, for patients.<br>
      Questions or feedback? <a href="mailto:help.seen.app@gmail.com">help.seen.app@gmail.com</a><br>
      © <span id="currentYear"></span> SEEN. All rights reserved.<br>
      SEEN is a patient communication tool and does not provide medical advice.
    </footer>
  </div>

  <!-- PWA Install Script -->
  <script>
    const installButton = document.getElementById("installButton");
    const yearSpan = document.getElementById("currentYear");
    let deferredPrompt;

    if (yearSpan) {
      yearSpan.textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    }

    window.addEventListener("beforeinstallprompt", (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      deferredPrompt = e;
      if (installButton) {
        installButton.style.display = "inline-flex";
      }
    });

    if (installButton) {
      installButton.addEventListener("click", () => {
        if (!deferredPrompt) return;
        deferredPrompt.prompt();
        deferredPrompt = null;
        installButton.style.display = "none";
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
